Dick Elliott https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dick_Elliott 0 For the U.S. senator with the same name, see Dick Elliott (politician).Richard "Dick" Elliott (April 30, 1886 – December 22, 1961) was an American character actor who played in over 240 films from the 1930s until the time of his death.
